desc: Revive Bathroom Supplies is located at 5/86 Greens Road, Dandenong South VIC Australia. We provide a massive range of products for you bathroom, kitchen and laundry at competitive prices. We are open to trade and general public. Whether you are building or renovating - we are happy to help!

layout.text: Our Impressive showroom boasts a massive selection of products to suit all budget and design preferences. We have fully fitted display bathrooms to inspire your design choices, along with many colour samples and product brochures so you can have all of the information you need to create your dream bathroom. Visit us at 5/86 Greens Road, Dandenong South VIC 3175
